text: Ulises de Jesús Tavares Reynoso (born April 29, 1993 in Tepatitlán de Morelos, Jalisco) is a Mexican professional footballer forward.Tavares es 100% fresero‚ am.com.mx, 30 January 2018 ==Club Career== ===Sonsonate=== Tavares signed with Sonsonate of the Salvadoran Primera División for the Apertura 2018 tournament. Sonsonate finished in eleventh position in the league table with 18 points.
